item.title: Code to large... Please help!
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

undo what they told you todo and do this

found this in one of my old folders
Purpose: Changes the max level very easily

Difficulty: 5

Assumed Knowledge: General Knowledge, and the xp which you have to work out.

Server Base: Cheezscape (Any)

Classes Modified: Client.java and Player.java

Open client.java and search for

	
	
for (int lvl = 1; lvl <= 135; lvl++) {
	
	
	
points += Math.floor((double)lvl + 300.0 * Math.pow(2.0, (double)lvl / 7.0));
	
	
	
output = (int)Math.floor(points / 4);
	
	
	
if (output >= exp) {
	
	
	
	
return lvl;
	
	
	
}
	
	
}
	
	
return 135;
	
}

Step 2;

Change all the 135’s to the number you want max level, I’ve gone 200 on my server. Too make it be level 200 for every stat, change all the 135’s to 200, and the 300.0 to 400.0, so it should look like this.

for (int lvl = 1; lvl <= 200; lvl++) {
	
	
	
points += Math.floor((double)lvl + 400.0 * Math.pow(2.0, (double)lvl / 7.0));
	
	
	
output = (int)Math.floor(points / 4);
	
	
	
if (output >= exp) {
	
	
	
	
return lvl;
	
	
	
}
	
	
}
	
	
return 200;
	
}

If there has been a TuT on this, please tell me, and you will have full credits, I just found this in my client.java
